<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>脈輪 on Lucky Stone</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E8%84%88%E8%BC%AA/</link><description>Recent content in 脈輪 on Lucky Stone</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E8%84%88%E8%BC%AA/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>海底輪完整指南：紅色根之輪如何打造安全感與接地能量</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E8%BC%AA%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E7%B4%85%E8%89%B2%E6%A0%B9%E4%B9%8B%E8%BC%AA%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%84%9F%E8%88%87%E6%8E%A5%E5%9C%B0%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E8%BC%AA%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E7%B4%85%E8%89%B2%E6%A0%B9%E4%B9%8B%E8%BC%AA%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%84%9F%E8%88%87%E6%8E%A5%E5%9C%B0%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;如果你曾經在凌晨三點醒來，胸口悶悶地，腦袋一片亂，又說不出到底在擔心什麼——那種「&lt;strong&gt;好像有什麼地方不安全&lt;/strong&gt;」的感覺，往往不是真的有事，而是你的**海底輪（Muladhara, Root Chakra）**正在跟你說話。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>喉輪完整指南：藍色表達之輪說出真實與創意之聲</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E5%96%89%E8%BC%AA%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E4%B9%8B%E8%BC%AA%E8%AA%AA%E5%87%BA%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%A6%E8%88%87%E5%89%B5%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%8B%E8%81%B2/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E5%96%89%E8%BC%AA%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E4%B9%8B%E8%BC%AA%E8%AA%AA%E5%87%BA%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%A6%E8%88%87%E5%89%B5%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%8B%E8%81%B2/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;你有沒有過這種經驗？心裡明明有滿滿的話想說，可是話到嘴邊就吞回去；或是會議上明明知道答案，卻在被點到那一刻喉嚨突然發乾、聲音變小、整個人縮了起來？&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶 x 眉心輪 &amp; 頂輪：一顆石頭，同時打開兩個靈性能量中心</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E8%84%88%E8%BC%AA%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E8%BC%AA%E8%88%87%E9%A0%82%E8%BC%AA%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E8%84%88%E8%BC%AA%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E8%BC%AA%E8%88%87%E9%A0%82%E8%BC%AA%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;大多數水晶只對應一個脈輪。紫水晶不一樣——它同時連結眉心輪和頂輪，也就是七脈輪體系裡最頂端的兩個能量中心。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>